name: Lethal Company
description: A co-op horror about scavenging at abandoned moons to sell scrap to the Company

name: Stardew Valey
description: You've inherited your grandfather's old farm plot in Stardew Valley. Armed with hand-me-down tools and a few coins, you set out to begin your new life. Can you learn to live off the land and turn these overgrown fields into a thriving home?

name: Valorant
description: VALORANT is a character-based 5v5 tactical shooter set on the global stage. Outwit, outplay, and outshine your competition with tactical abilities, precise gunplay, and adaptive teamwork.

name: Brawl Stars
description: Fast-paced 3v3 and Battle Royale matches Collect unique Brawlers. Play with your friends. Be the last one standing!

name: Genshin Impact
description: Travel across the seven nations and meet unique, powerful allies. Get more rare characters and weapons in the new version. Highlights: Creating Immersive Virtual World Experiences, Using Cutting-Edge Technologies.
